* Update NEWS and RELEASES files.

* Make sure all files are checked into RCS.

* Build and test the programs!

* Run "make clean".

* Copy entire directory to new release directory.

* In the copy, change permissions to make files writeable!

* Remove RCS directory and this file from the copy.

* Create tarball of new release.

* Create patch from previous release with "diff -urN".

* Sign tarball and patch.

* Place online on FTP server.

* Announce release on Freshmeat and gangplank homepage.
